data.description: Welcome to your slice of paradise! This expansive property offers endless opportunities for outdoor enthusiasts and nature lovers alike. Situated on a large lot with mature landscaping, this home is a true oasis of tranquility. Offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, open floor plan, and a flex space that can be used as a den, office or possible 4th bedroom! A seasonal creek meanders through the property, adding to the picturesque setting and providing a peaceful soundtrack. Enjoy evenings gathered around the cozy firepit, perfect for roasting marshmallows and sharing stories under the stars. The fully fenced-in property provides privacy and security, making it ideal for families and pets to roam and explore safely. Conveniently located close to Springville Elementary, this home offers the perfect blend of rural living and suburban convenience. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a place to create lasting memories with loved ones, this property will not disappoint! Schedule your showing today!
